          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王昭君上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别离泪涟，\n怎忍舍汉宫的辇。\n汉刘王，特煞柔软。"
        },
        {
          "character": "无端反贼弄朝权、王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文官齐齐，护送娘娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那文官齐齐全无用，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武将森森，护送娘娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是那，是那武将森森也是枉然。\n臣僚呵，于心怎安，于心怎安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "却将我红粉去和番、王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御弟王龙参见娘娘。愿娘娘千岁，千岁，千千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御弟免礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御弟，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "车辇可曾齐备？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐备多时。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐看辇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳。\n手下的，看辇哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王昭君上辇。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，手下的，娘娘上了辇了。一路上。要你们快快儿的，慢慢儿的，吓，跑哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（兵卒同允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王昭君 （山坡羊） 王昭君，一俟海枯石烂，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手挽着金镶玉嵌的琵琶儿一面。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼睁睁，眼睁睁盼不到南来雁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道昭君要见也无由见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "教奴家红粉亲自——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （同山坡羊） 去和番。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放声哭出雁门关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心在南朝身在北番。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要见刘王难上难。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王昭君 （山坡羊） 要见刘王只是难上难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启上娘娘：来此沙漠之地。车辇难行。请娘娘换了马罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐住辇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，手下的，住辇哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王昭君、兵卒同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马夫哪里，哪里？咳，马夫哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马夫上，跳。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奔腾千里荡尘埃，荡尘埃，渡水扒山紫雾开。拽断丝缰溜玉辔，火龙飞下九天\n来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马夫叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抬起头来。\n吓，你是娘个什么东西？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小的是个马夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是个马夫。可有良马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "良马俱已差尽。只剩得一匹劣马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "良马俱已差尽了，只剩得一匹劣马了。你可降得来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "降得来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳。马夫你与我降吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马夫降马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好马。真乃的好马。可有鞍辔？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有鞍辔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带下去备来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马夫允，备。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真乃人是衣衫，马是鞍辔。备上鞍辔益发好看了。马夫，带紧了。待你老爷试\n个试个。马夫，与你老爷加了鞭儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，咳，咳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王龙行，栽。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这样马，也是你娘娘骑跨得的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肚带不曾收紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肚带不曾收紧。待你老爷，煞个煞个肚带。\n娘娘有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王龙下。王昭君上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昭君扶玉鞍，上马啼红血。今日汉宫人，明朝胡地妾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马夫与我加鞭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，咳，咳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王昭君、马夫同行。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是哪里了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉陵了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王昭君 （楚江吟） 汉陵云横雾迷，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "撇下朔风吹透征衣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王昭君、马夫同行。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又是哪里了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汾关了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王昭君 （楚江吟） 人到汾关珠泪淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马为何不行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "南马不过北。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与我加鞭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳。咳，咳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王昭君、马夫同行。王龙换衣上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王昭君 （楚江吟） 慢说道人有思乡之意，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马呵，岂无恋国之心，何况人乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马到关前，它就步懒移。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只见北雁南飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见旷野云低。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "受洪福与天齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪曾受，哪曾受这风霜劳意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可曾望的见家乡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来路远了，望不见了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带转马头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（牧羊关） 哎呀，爹娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再见得我那爹娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "飘渺以似云飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "野花满地。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "总有那，巫山十二难寻觅。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "西风飒飒走胡尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "始信功劳在妇人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咬牙切齿恨奸臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若要相逢，若要相逢，一似海样深。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想主实指望，凤枕鸾衾同欢会。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都作了一样肚肠碎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内锣鼓响。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王昭君 （牧羊关） 又听得金鼓连天震地，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人似彪，马似龙驹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑白以似云飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "发似枯松，脸似黑漆，鼻似鹰钩，须卷山眉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王昭君 （牧羊关） 叫他们，一个一个下阵到关前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王昭君、马夫同下。二小番同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二小番",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "压捕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臊达子臊达子，\n娘娘嫌你们腥膻气。\n叫你们一个一个下阵到关前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二小番",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呜哩哇，哩哇，咯呜哩蒙董，\n吃杀乙呀，吱吱呀呀儿杀。\n呀。呀。吓得嘞呜杀呀。杀呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二小番",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "厄吉儿。你这个王八日的，打那个王八日的。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小番乙下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小番甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个蒙古。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不懂的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小番甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "照苏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不懂的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小番甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒙古你不懂的，照苏你也不懂的。亲爹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王龙允。小番甲打王龙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小番甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒙古，你不懂的；照苏，你也不懂的。叫你亲爹，你懂的。他那个王八日的，\n叫我这个王八日，打你这个王八日的。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小番甲打王龙。小番甲下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臊达子已去。\n娘娘有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马夫、王昭君同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御弟。我有五怨难舍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪五怨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王昭君",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第一来，难忘父母恩，\n第二来，难，难割舍同衾人。\n第四来，国家粮草都输尽。\n第五来，百万铁骑，为我昼夜辛勤。\n万年羞辱汉元君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "第三来，损害黎民、今日昭君舍了身、王龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "第三来，损害黎民、今日昭君舍了身、王龙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我想吓，他那里，也是个娘，娘吓，\n我这里，也是个娘，娘吓。\n我这里，也是国母唯。\n一般样的受用。\n何须愁闷，何须悲泪。\n我的娘娘吓，娘娘，娘娘。我的娘娘吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "他那里，也是国母唯、一般样的荣华、王昭君",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姣容貌，瘦损腰，\n手托香腮，泪珠流落。\n不作夷邦掌国人。\n又谁知助国无成。\n泪斑斑。带月披星。\n这头儿望不见汉长城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王昭君、王龙、马夫同下。）"
        }
      ],
